**Robot Terminal 1: Rebuild**
After files are copied/edited on the robot:


cd ~/gr4_ws
source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
colcon build --packages-select gr4_dropzone_mission gr4_camera_config
source install/setup.bash


**Robot Terminal 2: Nav2**
If Nav2 is not already running:


export ROS_DOMAIN_ID=138
source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
source ~/gr4_ws/install/setup.bash

ros2 launch articubot_one nav.launch.py map:=/home/rocket/maps/mekagangen.yaml


**Robot Terminal 3: Dropzone Mission**
This sends the approach goal and controls the manual stages:


export ROS_DOMAIN_ID=138
source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
source ~/gr4_ws/install/setup.bash

ros2 launch gr4_dropzone_mission dropzone_mission.launch.py


